This paper belongs to the field of computer science and criminology, specifically in the area of cybersecurity and online criminal activities. The paper discusses the darknet market supply chain, which involves the use of technology and online platforms for illegal drug trade. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.CY (Computers and Society). The paper also touches on the social and economic aspects of the drug trade, which could place it in the sub-categories of cs.SOC (Social and Information Networks) and cs.DL (Digital Libraries).
